# ih-experiment cookie for fetch-tags.mjs
# This is an A/B test flag (base64 JSON), NOT a session token.
# It doesn't expire and isn't IP-locked.
#
# How to obtain:
#   1. Open https://www.iherb.com in your browser
#   2. F12 → Application → Cookies → iherb.com
#   3. Find the "ih-experiment" cookie and copy its value
#
IH_EXPERIMENT=your_ih_experiment_cookie_value_here
